[{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-02-08-working-at-sharelike-asia","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"任職於 Sharelike.Asia","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"自從 10 月初退役後，就開始尋找工作，終於在 12 月塵埃落定。這段時間非常感謝這段期間協助我求職的朋友，尤其是幫我審閱履歷的 JC、Davy、FloatJ、小趴、松鼠、基爾、遊風等人，以及推薦我面試的均民（Microprogram）、白飄（Skyyer）、Davy（Sharelike）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經過諸多審思，最終決定任職於 Sharelike.Asia，並在 12 下旬開始上工。經過一個多月的摸索，目前在開發團隊的角色定位大概類似 Scrum Master，只不過自認為經驗還沒到達 Master 的程度，姑且自稱為 Agile Apprentice & Promter 吧。 =P"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"很高興有個環境能讓我實踐碩士時期所學，現在正在嘗試協助改善研發團隊的開發流程，以及每兩週分享一次敏捷開發相關主題。承蒙夥伴們的信任，讓我擔任這方面的角色，也期待未來與團隊一起共同成長。 = )"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"對於 Sharelike 有興趣的朋友，可以參照"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sharelike.asia/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"官方網站"}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]}]},"title_en":"Working at Sharelike.Asia","slug":"working-at-sharelike-asia","aliases":["任職於 Sharelike.Asia","Working at Sharelike.Asia"],"created_at":"2018-02-08T01:57:05.000Z","published_at":null,"updated_at":null,"tags":[],"moc":["Announcement"],"_type":"markdown","_id":"garden:legacy-articles:2018-02-08-working-at-sharelike-asia.md","_source":"garden","_file":"legacy-articles/2018-02-08-working-at-sharelike-asia.md","_extension":"md"},{"_path":"/legacy-articles/2018-02-19-citizenship-in-a-republic","_dir":"legacy-articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"en","_empty":false,"title":"老羅斯福演講：民主國家的公民權利","description":"","excerpt":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"以下摘錄自《Scrum，用一半的時間做兩倍的事》"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-1","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"1"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。原文為美國總統老羅斯福於 1910 年在巴黎索邦大學的演說「民主國家的公民權利」（Citizenship in a Republic）"},{"type":"element","tag":"sup","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fn-2","ariaDescribedBy":"footnote-label","dataFootnoteRef":true,"id":"user-content-fnref-2"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2"}]}]},{"type":"text","value":"。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"榮耀並不屬於批評的人，亦不屬於指出勇者如何失敗，或點出別人哪裡應該做的更好的人。榮耀屬於實際身處在競技場中、臉上沾滿塵土與血汗，仍英勇奮戰的勇者；他們會犯錯，而且一錯再錯，因為錯誤與缺失必會伴隨努力而來；但是他們都確切地知道要奮戰不懈、知道要充滿熱誠、全心投入；獻身於崇高的志業。他們最好的結局是終於功成名就；就算失敗，最差的下場只不過就是在勇敢奮戰後落敗。他們的定位，絕非那些冷漠懦弱、不知勝利與失敗為何物的人所能相提並論。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"附上摘自 Wiki 的原文版"},{"type":"element","tag":"span","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"^3"}]},{"type":"text","value":"："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"blockquote","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"It is not the critic who counts;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nnot the man who points out how the strong man stumbles,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nor where the doer of deeds could have done them better."},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nThe credit belongs to the man who is actually in the arena,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwhose face is marred by dust and sweat and blood;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwho strives valiantly; who errs,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwho comes short again and again,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nbecause there is no effort without error and shortcoming;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nbut who does actually strive to do the deeds;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwho knows great enthusiasms,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nthe great devotions;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwho spends himself in a worthy cause;"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nwho at the best knows in the end the triumph of high achievement,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nand who at the worst,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nif he fails,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nat least fails while daring greatly,"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\nso that his place shall never be with those cold and timid souls who neither know victory nor defeat."}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"section","props":{"className":["footnotes"],"dataFootnotes":true},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"className":["sr-only"],"id":"footnote-label"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Footnotes"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{"id":"user-content-fn-1"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"江裕真（譯）（2015）。SCRUM：用一半的時間做兩倍的事（原作者：Jeff Sutherland）。臺北市：遠見天下文化。（原著出版年：2014） "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"#user-content-fnref-1","ariaLabel":"Back to content","className":["data-footnote-backref"],"dataFootnoteBackref":true},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"↩"}]}]},{"type":"